                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ts-recon" value="RECONCILER — anti shadow-usage&#xa;rekonsiliasi: L3 (request L7)  vs  L1/L2 (event count)  vs  billing vendor" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F8CECC;strokeColor=#B85450;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="360" y="470" width="541" height="70" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ts-bill" value="Vendor Billing / Usage API&#xa;(OpenAI · Anthropic)&#xa;sumber kebenaran independen" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F5F5F5;strokeColor=#666666;fontSize=11;dashed=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1010" y="470" width="200" height="70" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ts-note" value="KELENGKAPAN (&#39;semua aktivitas&#39;): dijamin oleh L3 (egress backstop — semua trafik vendor wajib lewat) + rekonsiliasi vs billing vendor. Telemetri klien (L2) saja TIDAK cukup. Enforcement (block) hanya di lapisan in-band: L1, L2-hook, L3." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF2CC;strokeColor=#D6B656;fontStyle=2;align=left;fontSize=11;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="580" width="1170" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ts-legend" value="&lt;b&gt;Legenda lapisan:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;L1 Gateway&lt;/b&gt; — proxy wajib Chatbot; real-time, bisa menolak/redaksi sebelum keluar.&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;L2 OTel/Hooks&lt;/b&gt; — konteks kaya (tool, repo, paths); bergantung managed-settings terkunci.&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;L3 Egress/DLP/CASB&lt;/b&gt; — backstop jaringan untuk KEDUA platform; juga penangkap in-band konten Claude Code (ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=proxy.internal). Wajib mencakup web claude.ai.&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;L4 Compliance API&lt;/b&gt; — tarik/hapus konten sisi vendor; reaktif, retensi vendor terbatas.&lt;br&gt;• &lt;b&gt;Reconciler&lt;/b&gt; — bukti kelengkapan; selisih antar sumber ⇒ alert shadow-usage." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#9673A6;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="650" width="1170" height="150" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
